# Social Media Preview Image Instructions

To create an optimal social media preview image for ESO Log Insights, create a 1200x630 PNG image with:

## Design Elements:
- **Background**: Dark theme matching the app (background: #1a1a1a or similar)
- **Title**: "ESO Log Insights by NotaGuild" (prominent, white text)
- **Subtitle**: "Advanced Elder Scrolls Online Combat Log Analytics"
- **Visual Elements**: Charts, graphs, or combat-themed imagery
- **ESO Branding**: Use ESO-themed colors (gold, deep blue, fantasy elements)
- **Logo/Icon**: Include app icon or ESO-themed symbols

## Technical Requirements:
- **Dimensions**: 1200x630 pixels (Facebook/Twitter recommended ratio)
- **Format**: PNG with good compression
- **File Size**: Under 8MB (ideally under 1MB)
- **Safe Area**: Keep important text/elements in center 1200x630 area

## Color Palette (from app):
- Primary: #7289da (Discord blue)
- Background: #1a1a1a (dark)
- Accent: #38bdf8 (light blue)
- Text: #ffffff (white)
- Muted: #64748b (gray)

## Content Suggestions:
- Show sample damage charts/graphs
- Include ESO class icons
- Display sample DPS numbers
- Add "Free Combat Log Analysis" tagline
- Include website URL: bkrupa.github.io/eso-log-aggregator

Once created, replace this file with the actual PNG image.
